[MIKHAIL] Look at this
great amusement park!

00:21:20.905 --> 00:21:24.784 position:50% align:center
I bet it's fun, maybe
I can go to it someday.

00:21:24.868 --> 00:21:29.330 position:50% align:center
[footsteps continue]

00:21:29.414 --> 00:21:32.917 position:50% align:center
Oh, dear, Mademoiselle.
Not again!

00:21:41.301 --> 00:21:43.595 position:50% align:center
[MIKHAIL]
This won't do.

00:21:43.678 --> 00:21:48.350 position:50% align:center
I instructed you to bring
Monsieur Noé to me.

00:21:48.433 --> 00:21:51.895 position:50% align:center
Why can't you carry out
this one little request?

00:21:51.978 --> 00:21:55.690 position:50% align:center
I must warn you that,
if you fail to comply.

00:21:55.774 --> 00:21:58.777 position:50% align:center
then all that's left
is to use you as bait.

00:22:07.369 --> 00:22:10.955 position:50% align:center
Forgive me, Mademoiselle Domi.

